[4] Cholera - Uganda (Kampala)
Date: Tue 8 Jan 2019
Source: NTV [edited]
http://www.ntv.co.ug/news/national/Health-Ministry-confirms-Cholera-outbreak-in-Lubaga-Division/4522324-4925342-15gbo71/index.html


Preliminary investigations by the ministry of health show that there are cases of cholera in Lubaga division in Kampala. This comes after 3 people died and 8 others in Kironde zone in Kabowa were admitted to Naguru hospital over the weekend with a disease that residents and local health centers failed to properly diagnose.

